description: This file declares the exported API functions for the Slap Obj Entity Object in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) implementation, including function prototypes for creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization of the object.

methods.name: SlapCreateObjEntity
methods.description: Creates a new SLAP Obj Entity object with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: SlapOeoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new SLAP Obj Entity object with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: SlapOeoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the specified SLAP Obj Entity object.

methods.name: SlapOeoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrols or registers necessary sub-objects or dependencies for the SLAP Obj Entity.

methods.name: SlapOeoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the SLAP Obj Entity object, setting up necessary state.
